node.text:
More than the launch of unparalleled works of jewelry craft, @Bulgari's Magnifica High Jewelry collection is a celebration of rebirth. Honored through magnificent muses, music, and Milan, take a look at Bvlgari's latest high jewelry collection.
 
Models: @vittoria, @lilyaldridge @heconghc, @solangesmith and @blesnyaminher
Special Guests: @andreabocelliofficial @beatricevenezi
Project by @oma.eu
Director @tommaso.ottomano
DOP@ mrcodepa
Stylist @sagliogeraldine
Music @guazzonemarco 
Production @studio.april
#Bvlgari #BvlgariJewelry #BvlgariHighJewelry #BvlgariMagnifica #Milan

node.text: After making her #NYFW modeling debut at @ProenzaSchouler, @EllaEmhoff landed a knitwear collaboration with Batsheva Hay (@batshevadress). The 21-year-old student, model, and designer met up with Hay amid NYFW—and #GoodMorningVogue was there to capture their conversations about materials, fit, and texture, plus Ella's rise to fame in the wake of the inauguration of President Joe Biden and Emhoff’s step-mother, Kamala Harris, in January.

node.text: This month, Vogue joined forces with an army of photographers and models all around the globe—stable Zoom connections required, please!—and sent the best and brightest of the new collections via courier services everywhere from Beijing to Brazil, Lagos to Los Angeles. Our concept? Simple, glorious movement: After a year of stasis, immobility and lockdowns, we wanted to see spring fashion breaking free. These are the looks we love, shot by the photographers we adore, on the run and out for a walk, a swim, a dance. Tap the link in our bio to see more.

node.text:
Today, @KamalaHarris became the first woman of color ever sworn in as vice president of the United States.

To celebrate this moment, twelve young women discussing what it means to them to see a Black woman of Indian descent elected to the second-highest office in the land. “Every little girl sees that this is a country of possibility,” @KamalaHarris states in one address, and that sentiment is widely echoed. “She reminds me every day that I am capable and worthy of my wildest dreams,” says one participant.

Director @rombokob
Producer @aliwebb_producer
Casting Director: Rebecca Dealy
Archival Research: Manon Blackman
Editor @ann_lupo
GFX @horatiobaltz
Color @carlosfloresfilms
Mix @cstropko
Post Production @forager.tv

node.title: 12 Girls on What Kamala Harris Becoming Vice President Means to Them

node.text: Throughout the political tumult of 2020, @janayathefuture was one of the most prominent voices to become a source of healing and hope. Reflecting on this week’s events, Khan points out the lack of police presence at the Capitol, a fact that exposes, in their own words, “a clear double standard for how Black protestors have been treated over the past several years. What we know to be true is that there is a way that white rage is celebrated in this country and Black grief is criminalized.” To hear more, make sure to check out Khan’s Sunday Sermons, returning tomorrow 1/10  at 12PM PST on their account.

node.title: @janayathefuture on Moving Forward from the Capitol Riots

node.text: If you've been wondering what an average day in the life of @sabrinacarpenter is like, you're in luck. Last month, Vogue spent a jam-packed 24 hours with @sabrinacarpenter in California, where she split her time between the recording studio and getting ready for a (drive-in) movie premiere. Tap the link in our bio to watch the full video.

node.text: #GossipGirl star Emily Alyn Lind (@emilylind) has revealed her top #beautysecrets, from lash primer to how to master bold red lipstick. Tap the link in our bio to watch her full routine.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Vogue on August 03, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and sitting.

node.text: @Badgalriri's own mom actually worked in the beauty-and-fragrance industry, a fact she shared with us while speaking about Fenty Parfum, her brand's first fragrance. "She’d always get a lot of samples and introduce me to the scents when she came home,” she says. Fast forward to today, and the singer is now one of the first Black women to make a luxury fragrance in the South of France. Tap the link in our bio for all the details. Photographed by @MertAlas and @MacPiggott, Vogue, June 2018

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Vogue on August 03, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: Congratulations to @simonebiles! In her return to the Olympic competition, Biles won bronze in the balance beam final, taking home her seventh career Olympic medal, and tying her with Shannon Miller for the most by any gymnast in Team USA history. Photographed by @AnnieLeibovitz, Vogue, August 2020

Meet this year’s #MetGalachefs! For the first time ever, this year’s  @metcostumeinstitute’s #MetGala will feature a sustainable plant-based menu, featuring recipes from ten up-and-coming chefs based in New York City—and we’re giving you a sneak peek at who they are and the delicious recipes they have created. 

First up, @sophia_roe shares how to make her Plant-Based Nicoise Inspired Salad. Tap the link in our bio for the full recipe, and make sure to show us how you cooked like our #MetGalachefs.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Vogue on August 02, 2021 tagging @emrata, and @lesirenuse. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
The Amalfi Coast is an idyllic region that wraps around Italy’s southern cliffs and is a bucket list locale for many. Its roads wind romantically, the water is a calming azure, and the spaghetti alle vongole is plentiful—the epitome of la dolce vita. Places like @lesirenuse are a prime example of what the Amalfi Coast has to offer with breathtaking views and cute Italian charm to welcome you with open arms.

Tap the link in bio to discover all there is to eat, sleep, see and do on the beautiful Amalfi Coast.

#regram @emrata

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Vogue on August 01, 2021 tagging @ediebcampbell, @doutzen, and @adwoaaboah. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
The #MetGala is returning on September 13th and over the years, the @metmuseum’s annual Costume Institute Gala has become synonymous with striking displays of couture, rivaled only by the masterful coifs—decorated with subtle blooms and subversive headpieces alike—that accompany them. 

Click the link in bio for all the details you need to know. Photographed by @mrstreetpeeper

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Vogue on August 01, 2021 tagging @ladygaga, and @theguccimovie. May be an image of 1 person, standing and text that says 'SABRET'.

node.text:
After a year on Planet Chromatica, @ladygaga has made a welcome return to earth. More specifically, she’s followed her Oscar-nominated turn in A Star Is Born with a role in @theguccimovie, taking on the role of Italian socialite Patrizia Reggiani in Ridley Scott’s ’90s-set Lady Gucci biopic.

As the first trailer drops, we have rounded up everything revealed so far about the fashionable production at the link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Vogue on August 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, suit and outdoors.

node.text:
Just because it’s summer doesn’t mean you have to give up on outerwear altogether. There are plenty of jackets that are suitable for the season—a summer blazer among them. A lightweight fabric blazer is an ideal transitional piece for summer into fall, especially if you’re looking to pick up a polished piece or two if you’re headed back to the office in September.

If you are in search of the perfect light jacket for breezy evenings, or if you simply miss layering, find the best summer blazers to shop at the link in bio.

Photographed by @johncedmonds, Vogue, September 2020

node.text:
The Lake Como wedding of @giorgiagabriele, the founder and creative director of the fashion brand @wanderingofficial, and @off____white CEO @andrea___grilli was held under an archway of florals created by @vincenzodascanio for their lavish lakeside ceremony. To add to the elegance of the evening were the custom touches of the bride's wedding look. Giorgia worked with @virgilabloh on her gown, @aminamuaddi who designed her custom shoes.
Tap the link in bio to learn more about the Giorgia Gabriele and Andrea Grilli wedding.

Photos: @davidbastianoni

node.text:
If there’s one thing we know about @dualipa's style, it’s that she always takes a pick-and-mix approach to fashion from decades past. This week she released the video for her new track with the late rapper @realpopsmoke, “Demeanor.” The singer once again looked to the past for style inspiration—this time a little further back than usual.

Tap the link in bio to learn more about her Marie Antoinette inspired look.
